<p class="eyebrow">Compatibility</p>
<h1>Know exactly which call features are supported before migration.</h1>
<p class="lede">Every verb, attribute, REST resource, and caveat is published with a clear support status — supported, partial, roadmap, or unsupported — so you can see exactly what migrates cleanly before you cut traffic over.</p>
<p class="hero-actions">
	<a class="btn btn-primary" href="#matrix">View matrix</a>
	<a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/voiceml/validator/">Validate VoiceML</a>
	<a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/voiceml/migrate/">Migration guide</a>
</p>

<section id="matrix" class="section-block">
