				<tr>
					<th scope="row" rowspan="4"><strong>Messages</strong></th>
					<td><code>POST /Messages</code></td>
					<td><span role="img" class="compat-badge compat-supported" aria-label="Supported">✓</span></td>
					<td>Sends <code>Body</code> to <code>To</code> via the per-tenant SMS provider. Returns 201 with the Message resource (<code>status=sent</code> or <code>status=failed</code> with a Twilio-compatible <code>error_code</code>). When the provider isn't configured on the account, the row is persisted with <code>status=failed</code> and <code>error_code=21609</code>. For the native messaging product see <a href="/messaging/">VoiceTel Messaging</a>.</td>
				</tr>
